1
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:33,799
Greetings, my lord!

2
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,920
My lady is in the main hall.

3
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,159
Right this way.

4
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:37,959
Very well.

5
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,079
My lady!

6
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,200
My lady!

7
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:47,840
My lord,

8
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,760
it appears the ladies

9
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,200
have stepped into the courtyard.

10
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,400
Please sit.

11
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,519
I shall find them.

12
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,239
Aye.

13
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:07,680
Wanxue,

14
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,520
there's

15
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:10,680
something I have

16
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,080
long wished to tell you.

17
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:14,439
Go on, then.

18
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:17,479
Please stay.

19
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,680
My lord,

20
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,199
my lady's right there.

21
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:27,879
Aunt Jinzhao,

22
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:28,919
I have words

23
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,080
for Wanxue.

24
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:32,639
I ask that you bear witness.

25
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,879
The truth is...

26
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,360
My heart has long

27
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,319
belonged to another.

28
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,840
Hold your tongue!

29
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,000
You are

30
00:02:58,159 --> 00:02:59,159
betrothed to Wanxue.

31
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,319
Who is she?

32
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,560
Tell me!

33
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,960
Chen Xuanqing,

34
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,879
a man your age

35
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:18,080
knows the cost

36
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,759
of words.

37
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:22,639
Just tell me!

38
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,759
I won't.

39
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,039
I'm here to

40
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:32,680
give you the truth.

41
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:34,319
She is real.

42
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,360
If this is too much to bear

43
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:38,159
for you,

44
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,639
we should end it.

45
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,039
Enough!

46
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,280
Do you even

47
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,120
hear yourself?

48
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,199
As though she

49
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:46,319
owes you that mercy!

50
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,360
If another woman

51
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,319
held your heart,

52
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,280
you had no right to take her hand.

53
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,520
Wanxue,

54
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:55,879
come,

55
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:57,319
the Chens

56
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,759
owe you a reckoning.

57
00:03:59,400 --> 00:03:59,919
I'll see to it.

58
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:00,520
No.

59
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,319
If your heart

60
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,400
belongs to another,

61
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:05,919
why did you ask for my hand?

62
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,080
Was it after you

63
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:08,919
- proposed that you...
- I fell for her...

64
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,759
before the proposal.

65
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,279
Then why...

66
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,199
Because she is beyond my reach.

67
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,519
She always

68
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,040
has been.

69
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,879
She always will be.

70
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,199
Has reason left you entirely?

71
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,519
I hear you.

72
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:33,600
But I'm not breaking this off.

73
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,800
Let her live in your heart.

74
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,959
I'll live in your home.

75
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,680
Why'd you carry that weight?

76
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,160
Because

77
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,759
I've loved you my whole life.

78
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,079
The day my father told me

79
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,759
I was to be yours...

80
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:57,000
that was the first day I truly hoped.

81
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,839
Every time my stepmother was cruel,

82
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,800
every time I nearly broke,

83
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,639
I'd say to myself:

84
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,920
hold on, Wanxue.

85
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,480
He's waiting for you.

86
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,680
You're

87
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:11,480
almost there.

88
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,680
I won't give this up!

89
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,759
I won't! Never!

90
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:20,959
My dear,

91
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:21,920
listen...

92
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,360
Very well.

93
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:25,360
If that is your wish,

94
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:27,480
then

95
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:28,879
nothing changes.

96
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:32,879
Aunt Jinzhao,

97
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,360
what happened here today,

98
00:05:35,879 --> 00:05:36,639
let it stay here.

99
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,800
Some matters

100
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:40,079
are wiser left undisturbed.

101
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,199
Surely you agree.

102
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:47,519
Wanxue

103
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,279
has chosen.

104
00:05:53,879 --> 00:05:55,360
I will honor that.

105
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,920
But she deserves

106
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:02,079
to be chosen in return.

107
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:10,959
My lord...

108
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:11,800
I...

109
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,879
You saw nothing today.

110
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,040
Nothing.

111
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:16,399
Yes, my lord.

112
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,000
My lord,

113
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,920
perhaps...

114
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:23,519
I

115
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:25,120
should look into...

116
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,720
No,

117
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,279
there's nothing to look into.

118
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:29,839
Jinzhao keeps nothing from me.

119
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,040
I'll hear it from her.

120
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,519
Yes, my lord.

121
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:48,040
See to the men.

122
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,199
My lady.

123
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,120
What brings you here?

124
00:06:58,439 --> 00:06:59,800
Official business

125
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:00,560
brought me nearby.

126
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:01,560
Couldn't pass without stopping,

127
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,680
congratulations on

128
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,720
the new chapter.

129
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,600
Perfect timing.

130
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,279
I was just thinking of leaving.

131
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:13,720
Then

132
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,319
let's go home.

133
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,279
I still have things to attend to.

134
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,800
Go on inside.

135
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,240
Fine.

136
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:44,000
I thought he was a decent man.

137
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,160
I gave him that much.

138
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,839
How wrong I was.

139
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,519
My lady,

140
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,920
does my lord

141
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:53,680
need to know this?

142
00:07:54,079 --> 00:07:55,040
He does.

143
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:58,319
But I know his temper.

144
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,720
The moment this comes to light,

145
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,720
he'll have the betrothal

146
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:03,759
dissolved by morning.

147
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,000
And Wanxue's

148
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,160
made her choice and

149
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,399
nothing will move her from it.

150
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:11,279
This is what we do.

151
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,319
Pass the word:

152
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:14,800
Xuanqing does not set foot

153
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,680
in this courtyard.

154
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,160
Not without

155
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,240
my leave.

156
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,360
And I want

157
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,279
eyes on him.

158
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,800
Morning greetings,

159
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,600
meals,

160
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:28,000
wherever he shows up,

161
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,279
I disappear.

162
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:30,879
Keep us apart.

163
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:32,679
Yes, my lady.

164
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,720
Bamboo shoots here,

165
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,799
Madam will want them near.

166
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:36,320
Right here.

167
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,399
Yes, my lady.

168
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,440
Now see what's left

169
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,440
in the kitchen,

170
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,120
and bring it all out.

171
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:42,679
My lady.

172
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,799
Stop dawdling.

173
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,240
I want this table set properly.

174
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:51,600
Darling,

175
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,840
keeping busy

176
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,919
these days?

177
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:58,039
Somewhat,

178
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,440
Grandmother.

179
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,039
The academy

180
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:01,000
is compiling the imperial codex.

181
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,200
Busier than before,

182
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:04,080
but

183
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:05,039
manageable.

184
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,120
Good.

185
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:10,120
Mrs. Yu paid us a visit

186
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,200
the other day

187
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,240
and brought up your wedding.

188
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,360
Madam,

189
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:20,840
my lady

190
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,960
tired herself out today.

191
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,759
She's feeling unwell.

192
00:09:24,279 --> 00:09:26,080
She sends her apologies for this evening.

193
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,559
If she's unwell,

194
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:30,720
she should rest.

195
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,519
She can skip morning greetings as well.

196
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:34,679
Yes, Madam.

197
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:39,840
Eat.

198
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,679
What hour is it?

199
00:10:00,399 --> 00:10:02,519
Do you have to leave already?

200
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,039
Not yet.

201
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,759
You've been run ragged lately.

202
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,039
Aye.

203
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:16,559
It's flood season.

204
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,200
Every waterway needs reinforcing,

205
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:20,720
and every local official

206
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,159
has come begging for funds.

207
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,679
You get

208
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:25,759
no sleep as it is.

209
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,200
Honestly,

210
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:31,360
just stay at the office

211
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:34,240
and spare yourself the ride.

212
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:48,320
What?

213
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:53,679
What's with

214
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:55,879
the long face?

215
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:58,440
You'd have me sleep at the office.

216
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:02,279
You think I want you gone?

217
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,320
I'd keep you here

218
00:11:05,639 --> 00:11:06,759
every day if I could.

219
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,919
We haven't had

220
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,000
a single moment

221
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,519
to ourselves

222
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,919
since the wedding.

223
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:18,919
Your weariness pains my heart.

224
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,440
Then let us take that moment now.

225
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,399
[Gallivanting past curfew…]

226
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:33,480
[Pray, what does the law prescribe?]

227
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,159
[His Majesty made an exception.]

228
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,480
[Such favor bestowed upon my lord!]

229
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,960
[Still harboring a grudge?]

230
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,039
[Grudge?]

231
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,440
[You ought to be held to account.]

232
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:45,399
[For what offense?]

233
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:47,399
[Rousing me before daybreak,]

234
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,000
[only to sulk at me.]

235
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:50,639
[Still stewing, hm?]

236
00:11:50,639 --> 00:11:51,600
[Yes,]

237
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:52,720
[for quite a bit longer.]

238
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,759
[I await your verdict]

239
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,840
[with pleasure.]

240
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:36,879
[Look at her.]

241
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,519
[Not a shadow on her face.]

242
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,039
[Whatever she hides within,]

243
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,720
[she has made peace with it.]

244
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,240
[So let her keep it.]

245
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,639
My lady!

246
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:36,759
My lady,

247
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:37,960
where did you

248
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:38,879
disappear to?

249
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,240
I knocked for an age,

250
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,080
nothing.

251
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:42,000
I opened the door,

252
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,960
empty.

253
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,360
You nearly stilled my heart.

254
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:49,080
My lord took me out...

255
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,120
At that hour?

256
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,360
My lord and his wild notions.

257
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,519
Count his wild notions

258
00:13:56,879 --> 00:13:58,360
and you'll be occupied

259
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,240
all day.

260
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:00,960
My lady,

261
00:14:01,759 --> 00:14:02,559
HE...

262
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,840
left this morning.

263
00:14:04,159 --> 00:14:04,559
Come then.

264
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,080
Let's greet Madam.

265
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,600
She went straight

266
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,080
to Grandmother

267
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,039
the moment I walked out?

268
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,279
Yes,

269
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:14,320
Master...

270
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,320
There's more.

271
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:18,039
Madam has passed

272
00:14:18,519 --> 00:14:19,159
your betrothal arrangements

273
00:14:19,159 --> 00:14:20,720
to Lady Jinzhao.

274
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:22,879
What?

275
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,919
Hasn't this always

276
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:27,320
fallen to Lady Xianlan?

277
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,679
Why's she meddling in it now?

278
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:30,440
I was at a loss too.

279
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:32,080
Word is

280
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,519
she asked for it herself.

281
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,840
Of course she did.

282
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,559
I'd say the same.

283
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:38,559
Master,

284
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:40,240
she wants walls between you,

285
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,480
high ones.

286
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,360
You should build some of your own.

287
00:14:43,919 --> 00:14:45,840
Once Lady Yu enters this house,

288
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,720
one wrong step and it all falls apart.

289
00:14:48,759 --> 00:14:49,799
Gu Jinzhao...

290
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,279
Master,

291
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:55,840
where are you going...

292
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,679
Not another step.

293
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,559
If it's Lord Chen you seek,

294
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:13,960
he's in the study.

295
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:15,679
These are the lady's quarters.

296
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:16,960
It would not

297
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,159
be proper.

298
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,279
I wish to consult Aunt

299
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,919
on certain matters.

300
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:27,639
With your scholarly eminence,

301
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:28,559
what could you

302
00:15:28,559 --> 00:15:29,559
possibly need to consult her about?

303
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:31,360
She has buried herself

304
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,559
in your betrothal

305
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,279
every single day.

306
00:15:34,759 --> 00:15:35,799
She's not receiving visitors.

307
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,279
I'll have to ask you to leave.

308
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:38,960
Very well.

309
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:41,679
Very well...

310
00:17:34,519 --> 00:17:35,319
Five...

311
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:36,799
Six...

312
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,240
Why is Prince Ningan

313
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,519
still sitting on our money?

314
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:53,119
We've sent word three times.

315
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,400
The truth is,

316
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,039
there's nothing left.

317
00:17:56,519 --> 00:17:57,799
The whole household

318
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,839
is at each other's throats

319
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,480
over whatever scraps remain.

320
00:18:01,759 --> 00:18:03,519
And the prince spends

321
00:18:03,519 --> 00:18:04,640
faster than he earns.

322
00:18:05,519 --> 00:18:06,680
In my humble opinion,

323
00:18:06,799 --> 00:18:08,400
they won't be

324
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:09,960
paying us back any time soon.

325
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:11,160
That said...

326
00:18:11,519 --> 00:18:12,799
it's still a prince's house.

327
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,000
A name like that doesn't lose

328
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,319
all its value at once.

329
00:18:15,559 --> 00:18:16,640
What are you suggesting?

330
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,359
Lady Chen

331
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,359
was being rude

332
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:22,000
to you.

333
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,559
I've been

334
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,759
thinking of a way

335
00:18:25,759 --> 00:18:27,000
to make it sting her back.

336
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:28,720
How would you make that happen?

337
00:18:29,799 --> 00:18:30,799
The lord has returned.

338
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:38,720
What are you two

339
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:39,880
plotting over here?

340
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:40,680
My lord.

341
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:44,079
Plotting against Lord Chen.

342
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,160
Now that's something

343
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:47,480
worth plotting!

344
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,200
By all means, carry on.

345
00:18:53,079 --> 00:18:53,799
Go on.

346
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,319
It's opening day.

347
00:19:02,799 --> 00:19:04,200
Why come fetch me?

348
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:05,720
You could've just waited there.

349
00:19:06,519 --> 00:19:07,000
Ah,

350
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:08,039
Lian's wedding

351
00:19:08,279 --> 00:19:10,359
to Yao Wenxiu draws near.

352
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,799
Will you arrive the night before,

353
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:15,720
or on the morning itself?

354
00:19:16,319 --> 00:19:17,440
The morning.

355
00:19:17,759 --> 00:19:18,640
My presence

356
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,200
would bring them no joy.

357
00:19:23,039 --> 00:19:23,759
Jinzhao,

358
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,559
I must ask a favor of you.

359
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,200
Go on.

360
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,799
The Mus wish to…

361
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,839
send a formal proposal.

362
00:19:35,039 --> 00:19:35,680
Pardon?

363
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,599
Speak up.

364
00:19:39,599 --> 00:19:41,440
They want to send the betrothal gifts!

365
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:44,720
Only… not at Daxin.

366
00:19:45,039 --> 00:19:46,640
Could they come to

367
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:47,640
the Chen estate instead?

368
00:19:49,039 --> 00:19:49,839
Well, well,

369
00:19:50,599 --> 00:19:51,079
so he isn't

370
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:53,039
so dull-witted as before?

371
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,640
He improves

372
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:57,680
upon

373
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,119
acquaintance.

374
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,839
Does he now?

375
00:20:04,279 --> 00:20:05,200
Is Wanxue

376
00:20:05,319 --> 00:20:07,200
also soon to be blessed?

377
00:20:09,279 --> 00:20:09,839
She is.

378
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,200
We'll set a date

379
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,440
with the Yu family shortly,

380
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:18,640
most likely

381
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:20,240
still this year.

382
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:31,160
My ladies,

383
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,640
Prince Ningan's men

384
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:33,720
have besieged

385
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,240
the whole place!

386
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,799
Mr. Luo is holding them off outside!

387
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:38,359
I've never

388
00:20:39,559 --> 00:20:40,799
crossed paths with him.

389
00:20:43,279 --> 00:20:43,759
Go with

390
00:20:44,079 --> 00:20:44,839
Mr. Ping,

391
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,000
find out what this is.

392
00:20:46,759 --> 00:20:47,599
I shall keep close

393
00:20:47,799 --> 00:20:48,680
and watch.

394
00:20:48,759 --> 00:20:49,240
Right.

395
00:20:53,839 --> 00:20:55,680
We keep a clean record, my lord.

396
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,519
Taxes paid on time,

397
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:58,279
trade honest and aboveboard.

398
00:20:58,519 --> 00:21:00,240
There must be some misunderstanding.

399
00:21:02,319 --> 00:21:03,039
My lady!

400
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:03,839
Mr. Ping.

401
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:05,920
This is Lord Lai,

402
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:07,480
steward to His Highness

403
00:21:07,839 --> 00:21:08,440
Prince Ningan.

404
00:21:08,559 --> 00:21:09,039
Allow me

405
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,000
to present Lady Gu Lan,

406
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,079
who owns

407
00:21:11,319 --> 00:21:12,240
this restaurant.

408
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:14,519
Greetings, my lord.

409
00:21:15,279 --> 00:21:16,440
Lady Gu Lan?

410
00:21:17,359 --> 00:21:18,480
How curious.

411
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,000
We were told the proprietress

412
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,920
is Lady Chen,

413
00:21:22,079 --> 00:21:23,400
wife of Lord Chen Yanyun.

414
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:26,359
So you are… what, exactly?

415
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,680
Lady Chen is my sister.

416
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,359
I manage this establishment

417
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:31,599
on her behalf,

418
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:32,759
my lord.

419
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,359
Fine then.

420
00:21:35,039 --> 00:21:35,680
A simple matter.

421
00:21:36,119 --> 00:21:36,960
We have a performer

422
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,319
in our employ,

423
00:21:38,519 --> 00:21:39,559
Xia Xiaohan.

424
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,319
A gifted talent on the stage,

425
00:21:42,079 --> 00:21:42,759
sharp-witted

426
00:21:43,039 --> 00:21:43,880
and pleasing to the eye,

427
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,880
well-favored by His Highness.

428
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,359
Not long ago,

429
00:21:47,359 --> 00:21:48,279
he disappeared

430
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,839
without a word to anyone.

431
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,759
I had inquiries made,

432
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:55,480
and every trail

433
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,279
leads to

434
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:59,119
your door.

435
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,559
Deliver him to me,

436
00:22:01,559 --> 00:22:03,079
my lady.

437
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,680
My patience wears thin.

438
00:22:07,559 --> 00:22:08,759
Is not Xia Xiaohan a man?

439
00:22:09,079 --> 00:22:09,720
They keep a man hidden within?

440
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,279
What is happening?

441
00:22:11,559 --> 00:22:12,359
My lord.

442
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:15,200
We serve women only.

443
00:22:15,759 --> 00:22:17,119
Every servant,

444
00:22:17,119 --> 00:22:18,359
every soul on the staff,

445
00:22:18,559 --> 00:22:19,519
a woman.

446
00:22:20,079 --> 00:22:21,920
The man you seek

447
00:22:22,359 --> 00:22:24,000
could not be concealed here.

448
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,839
I fear you've been led astray.

449
00:22:26,079 --> 00:22:26,599
My lady,

450
00:22:27,279 --> 00:22:28,359
are you really prepared

451
00:22:28,519 --> 00:22:30,319
to stand against His Highness?

452
00:22:30,759 --> 00:22:31,240
I wouldn't dare.

453
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,279
I only find it curious,

454
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:34,279
today of all days, our first day open,

455
00:22:34,559 --> 00:22:35,880
and you arrive with men

456
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,079
to surround the place.

457
00:22:37,359 --> 00:22:38,960
That is a remarkable coincidence.

458
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:40,200
I had no knowledge

459
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,720
of your opening.

460
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:44,359
I serve only His Highness' command.

461
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,319
Give me the man,

462
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,599
or

463
00:22:48,039 --> 00:22:49,279
this stops being a conversation.

464
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:50,000
Men,

465
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:50,920
search the premises.

466
00:22:51,519 --> 00:22:52,039
Hold,

467
00:22:54,279 --> 00:22:54,880
my lord.

468
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:57,839
Put aside my sister's marriage

469
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,240
to Lord Chen.

470
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,640
Your men storm my premises

471
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,039
on our opening day.

472
00:23:03,319 --> 00:23:04,079
If word of this spreads,

473
00:23:04,079 --> 00:23:05,200
our reputation will be ruined.

474
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,440
Find him, and I shall

475
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:09,079
go with you gladly,

476
00:23:09,079 --> 00:23:10,119
without a word of protest.

477
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,279
But if he isn't here,

478
00:23:13,039 --> 00:23:13,880
His Highness

479
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,480
owes us

480
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,480
a full reckoning.

481
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,319
Every loss

482
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:19,759
we suffer today

483
00:23:20,079 --> 00:23:21,720
shall be laid at his feet.

484
00:23:22,039 --> 00:23:24,240
These good people are my witnesses.

485
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:25,960
Do we have an accord,

486
00:23:26,519 --> 00:23:27,400
my lord?

487
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:29,599
We have orders from above!

488
00:23:29,759 --> 00:23:30,440
Step aside!

489
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:31,119
Clear the street.

490
00:23:31,559 --> 00:23:32,559
Official business.

491
00:23:32,559 --> 00:23:33,960
Move aside or be arrested!

492
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,960
We have orders to search

493
00:23:40,599 --> 00:23:42,440
these premises for a fugitive!

494
00:23:43,079 --> 00:23:43,519
Move!

495
00:23:59,200 --> 00:23:59,839
Jinzhao,

496
00:24:00,279 --> 00:24:01,920
the magistrate's men are upon us.

497
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,240
Shall we send word to Lord Chen?

498
00:24:11,119 --> 00:24:11,759
My lady.

499
00:24:13,039 --> 00:24:13,640
Mr. Ping.

500
00:24:14,559 --> 00:24:15,759
Spare no coin,

501
00:24:16,039 --> 00:24:17,079
get the leader

502
00:24:17,079 --> 00:24:18,240
into a suite.

503
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,480
I would have words with him.

504
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:20,559
My lady.

505
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:31,240
Sir,

506
00:24:31,519 --> 00:24:32,200
right this way.

507
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:50,599
Leave us.

508
00:24:50,799 --> 00:24:51,240
At once.

509
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,880
My lady extends such courtesy,

510
00:24:56,839 --> 00:24:58,200
it is only right

511
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,480
that I return it.

512
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,119
My knowledge of the matter

513
00:25:01,119 --> 00:25:02,440
is shallow at best.

514
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:03,599
Yet

515
00:25:03,759 --> 00:25:05,039
one thought lingers:

516
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,079
Has your mistress

517
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:07,880
recently made an enemy,

518
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:08,920
one with power

519
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,839
enough to move against

520
00:25:11,119 --> 00:25:12,559
a lady of her status?

521
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,000
Such enemies aren't common.

522
00:25:16,119 --> 00:25:16,640
Mr. Ping.

523
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,519
Forgive me,

524
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,400
duty calls.

525
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,160
Good day!

526
00:25:30,559 --> 00:25:31,920
Once you've weathered

527
00:25:32,079 --> 00:25:32,640
enough storms,

528
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,640
you stop flinching at rain.

529
00:25:35,079 --> 00:25:35,559
My love!

530
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,599
Why are you here?

531
00:25:39,359 --> 00:25:40,319
Where else would I be?

532
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,279
Chen Yi told me

533
00:25:54,279 --> 00:25:55,039
everything.

534
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:56,599
I'm coming with you

535
00:25:56,599 --> 00:25:57,279
to the magistrate.

536
00:25:57,720 --> 00:25:58,680
It won't be necessary.

537
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,440
I know what this is,

538
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:02,599
and the magistrate

539
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:04,279
isn't where the problem started.

540
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,160
Return to

541
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,440
your work.

542
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:08,839
Do not trouble yourself.

543
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,680
That is not

544
00:26:12,319 --> 00:26:13,400
how this works.

545
00:26:14,079 --> 00:26:14,640
You've

546
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,960
weathered worse in business.

547
00:26:16,279 --> 00:26:16,960
But when

548
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:18,559
it involves a prince

549
00:26:18,559 --> 00:26:19,359
and the magistrates,

550
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:21,000
that's where I step in.

551
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,039
Ease your mind.

552
00:26:23,559 --> 00:26:24,640
I've handled men

553
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:25,759
with seals

554
00:26:25,960 --> 00:26:27,319
on my own.

555
00:26:28,119 --> 00:26:29,160
More than once!

556
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:30,680
And if I

557
00:26:30,839 --> 00:26:32,200
start letting your name

558
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,440
open doors for me,

559
00:26:33,559 --> 00:26:34,440
I'm not

560
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,920
a merchant anymore.

561
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:36,839
I'll be your liability.

562
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,960
A single whisper of this in the right ear

563
00:26:39,319 --> 00:26:40,200
could bring you ruin.

564
00:26:43,599 --> 00:26:44,359
No need

565
00:26:44,519 --> 00:26:46,039
to shoulder this alone.

566
00:26:46,799 --> 00:26:47,680
Yes, my love.

567
00:26:55,559 --> 00:26:56,000
Go,

568
00:26:56,119 --> 00:26:57,640
let nothing stop you.

569
00:26:58,400 --> 00:26:59,160
I shall not be long.

570
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:04,440
My lord,

571
00:27:04,799 --> 00:27:05,480
this is

572
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:06,519
unconscionable!

573
00:27:07,039 --> 00:27:08,200
They have truly moved against my lady!

574
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:12,720
A man of

575
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:15,160
Zheng Xiaoyou's standing…

576
00:27:15,839 --> 00:27:16,720
reduced to running errands

577
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,039
for Wang Xuanfan?

578
00:27:19,599 --> 00:27:20,079
So be it.

579
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,319
He's the one

580
00:27:24,079 --> 00:27:25,119
I start with!

581
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:51,400
My lord,

582
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,400
I must excuse myself.

583
00:27:56,119 --> 00:27:58,119
My wife opened her establishment today,

584
00:27:58,839 --> 00:28:01,119
yet someone has moved against her.

585
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,240
The authorities have sealed the doors.

586
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:09,799
Who would dare?

587
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,119
Have the authorities

588
00:28:12,799 --> 00:28:13,720
lost all sense of honor?

589
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:14,720
My lord,

590
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:16,960
I wonder the same.

591
00:28:17,759 --> 00:28:19,240
Whoever is behind this

592
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,160
fears no reprisal.

593
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:21,559
Someone high in power

594
00:28:22,079 --> 00:28:23,359
must be holding their leash.

595
00:28:24,279 --> 00:28:25,039
But things

596
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:26,839
have a way of coming to light.

597
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,240
And the man pulling the strings...

598
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:48,799
Why are you looking at me?

599
00:28:49,359 --> 00:28:50,799
Why do you ask, my lord?

600
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,880
What a curious man.

601
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,119
His wife

602
00:29:16,599 --> 00:29:17,759
courted disaster all on her own.

603
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:19,319
What has that to do with me?

604
00:29:26,839 --> 00:29:29,400
Yanyun didn't rise to

605
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:31,160
where he stands

606
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,960
so his wife could give the city

607
